Map Name: gg_mr_max

Version: 1

Created By: Paul '[MalReynolds]' Elliott

Email: whde2000@yahoo.co.uk

Trying to make a map since my initial set has proved difficult, but recently i found my muse who has inspired me to make this map. It's a small map meant to promote fast gun play. So hopefully i've succeeded with that.

Dev textures from FPSBanana http://www.fpsbanana.com/ by 

Chris528. Thanks for the textures.

Spawn Points: 40

I added the .nav to the .bsp file, so hopefully it should work, but i've never done it this way before. Any problems let me know :)
